name: Soap and candle making
shortDesc: A soap and candle making workshop is an event where participants learn the art of creating their own personal care products and decorative candles.
longDesc:
A soap and candle making workshop is an event where participants learn the art of creating their own personal care products and decorative candles. 
In the workshop, attendees are typically taught the basic principles of soap and candle making, such as the chemistry behind it, the proper use of equipment and ingredients, and various techniques for customizing their products. 
By the end of the workshop, participants usually have the skills and knowledge needed to continue making soap and candles at home.

Attending a soap and candle making workshop is not only a fun and creative experience, but it also offers the opportunity to make high-quality, natural and customizable products that can be used daily. You'll have the chance to learn new skills, meet like-minded people, and take home your own handmade creations. 
Plus, the workshop provides a great opportunity to create unique and thoughtful gifts for friends and family. 

Join us for an unforgettable day of learning, creativity, and self-expression. Sign up today!
